Hiding potentaily dangerous information with helmet using the hide powered by command;

first uninstall helmet:
npm uninstall helmet
refresh on terminal

install helmet 2.3.0
 refresh
 
 go to myapp.js
 app.use(helmet.hidePoweredBy());
 
 to further decieve hacker
 
 app.use(helmet.hidePoweredBy({setTo: 'PHP 4.2.0'}));
